projectGridLines.title: Brief of project/assignment
projectGridLines.description:
Brief of project/assignment

Job Description: Students offered Internship with Oloid will need

to fulfill the following functions

1. Understand the assigned Products and use cases

2. Learn the tech competencies and skillsets required for

contributing to the products

3. Fulfill tasks assigned to them from their immediate managers.


Following is the list of technologies Oloid uses and requires the

student to either understand beforehand or learn during the

course of internship

1. Nodejs

2. React

3. Identity Access and Management

4. AWS
